#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given a general exponential form of y = b*m^x for a curve fit, calculates b "
"if TRUE or forces b to be 1 and only calculates the m values if FALSE."
msgstr ""
"Givet den eksponentielle model y = b·m^x for en kurvetilpasning beregnes b, "
"hvis TRUE; hvis FALSE sættes b til 1, og kun m beregnes."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given a general linear form of y = m*x+b for a curve fit, calculates b if "
"TRUE or forces b to be 0 and only calculates the m values if FALSE, i.e. "
"forces the curve fit to pass through the origin."
msgstr ""
"Givet den lineære model y = m·x + b for en kurvetilpasning beregnes b ved "
"TRUE, mens b sættes til 0 ved FALSE, og kun m beregnes, hvilket tvinger "
"kurven til at gå gennem origo."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given partial data about a linear trend, calculates various parameters about "
"the ideal linear trend using the least-squares method."
msgstr ""
"Ud fra delvise data om en lineær tendens beregnes parametre for den ideelle "
"lineære tendens ved hjælp af mindste kvadraters metode."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given partial data about an exponential growth curve, calculates various "
"parameters about the best fit ideal exponential growth curve."
msgstr ""
"Ud fra delvise data om en eksponentiel vækstkurve beregnes parametre for den "
"bedst passende eksponentielle vækstkurve."

